thread.title: Jacksonski

author: Jacksonski
title: Jacksonski
text: The product was exactly as advertised. It was delivered super fast. There was some damage to the packaging but given the product is steel, it didn't matter. My only complaint was that one box was full of tiny metal shavings which spilled all over the place when I opened the box. A leftover from manufacturing no doubt. Nothing a few magnets and some curious young boys couldn't fix.
